To generate the txt from the markdown use something like:

mmark -xml2 -page draft-ietf-dnsop-dns-capture-format-00.md > draft-ietf-dnsop-dns-capture-format-00.xml && xml2rfc --text draft-ietf-dnsop-dns-capture-format-00.xml && rm draft-ietf-dnsop-dns-capture-format-00.xml

mmark can be found here https://github.com/miekg/mmark